[DhtmlXQ_result]红胜[/DhtmlXQ_result]
[DhtmlXQ_open]C03 中炮七路马对屏风马[/DhtmlXQ_open]
[DhtmlXQ_remark]阎文清[/DhtmlXQ_remark]
[DhtmlXQ_author]弈聪[/DhtmlXQ_author]
